title: Requiem for the Sun - Elizabeth Haydon
description:
Written by Elizabeth Haydon
Read by Erin Jones
Format: MP3
Unabridged

It has been three years since their devastating battle, and peace has settled across their land. But to the south an empire lies ready to crumble. When the dowager empress dies along with her successor, a great war breaks out, threatening to overwhelm the known world.

This is the fourth in the Symphony of Ages series. Like the others, I've cleaned up the audio, chapterized the book, and updated all the tags. This series is, for me, a test to see how much the community likes this sort of thing. If it gets a strong positive response, I've got tons of other books I've done the same thing too I'd love to share
